    <item>
      <title>如果税收增加，七分之一的英国公司会考虑离开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/one-in-seven-uk-companies-consider-leaving-if-taxes-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民意调查机构 Savanta 的一项调查显示，如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 在本月晚些时候的预算中提高企业的税收负担，七分之一的英国商界领袖会考虑将公司业务迁往海外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/one-in-seven-uk-companies-consider-leaving-if-taxes-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:37:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回拜登政府在德克萨斯州堕胎案中的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/supreme-court-spurns-biden-administration-in-texas-abortion-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在一场有关堕胎权的纠纷中驳回了拜登政府的诉求，维持了上诉法院在有关医院急诊室能否提供堕胎服务的斗争中做出的有利于德克萨斯州的裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/supreme-court-spurns-biden-administration-in-texas-abortion-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:35:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回宾夕法尼亚州共和党选民登记上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/supreme-court-rebuffs-pennsylvania-gop-voter-registration-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院驳回了对总统乔·拜登三年前提出的选民登记倡议的质疑，避免了 11 月大选前夕爆发激烈的政治斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/supreme-court-rebuffs-pennsylvania-gop-voter-registration-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市副市长菲尔·班克斯在联邦调查中辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nyc-deputy-mayor-phil-banks-steps-down-amid-federal-probes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市负责公共安全的副市长菲尔·班克斯辞职，成为市政厅面临联邦调查期间亚当斯政府第六位下台或宣布离职计划的高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nyc-deputy-mayor-phil-banks-steps-down-amid-federal-probes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院因美国司法部秘密特朗普逮捕令驳回马斯克的 X 申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/musk-s-x-rejected-by-supreme-court-over-secret-doj-trump-warrant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院驳回了伊隆·马斯克旗下 X 公司的上诉，避免了因司法部秘密搜查令搜查唐纳德·特朗普社交媒体账户相关记录而引发的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/musk-s-x-rejected-by-supreme-court-over-secret-doj-trump-warrant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯导弹击中一艘载有出口玉米的船只</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据基辅基础设施部称，一艘满载乌克兰出口谷物的散货船上周末在敖德萨地区遭到俄罗斯导弹袭击而受损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙政府与反对派继续就预算进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/portugal-s-government-opposition-continue-talks-about-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙少数党政府表示，正在等待与反对党社会党进行谈判，然后提出 2025 年预算的最终提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/portugal-s-government-opposition-continue-talks-about-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 12:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果将严厉打击购买冲突矿物的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/congo-to-clamp-down-on-companies-buying-conflict-minerals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国计划严厉打击从其饱受战争蹂躏的东部地区购买或采购矿产的公司，该地区的走私活动加剧了世界上最严重的人道主义危机之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/congo-to-clamp-down-on-companies-buying-conflict-minerals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 12:36:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国财政部长承诺预算将遵守欧盟规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/french-finance-minister-promises-budget-will-respect-eu-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长安托万·阿尔芒表示，政府将在本周提交一份遵守欧盟规则的预算，以安抚欧盟合作伙伴和市场对法国失控赤字的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/french-finance-minister-promises-budget-will-respect-eu-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 08:25:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯在一年战争后冲突中向以色列发射火箭弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-strikes-across-gaza-to-thwart-renewed-hamas-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一年的战争，战斗进一步升级，以色列轰炸了加沙地带与哈马斯有关的多个目标后，哈马斯向特拉维夫发射了多枚火箭弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-strikes-across-gaza-to-thwart-renewed-hamas-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
